{"tid":1867004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動post］10.7全力撐醫護！！！開放討論","createTime":"2020-02-07T03:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T04:20:09.000Z","uid":227979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8948b56c1845e25dd212dc936003bbec62400b56","tid":1867004,"uid":227979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:58:45.000Z","msg":"大家夠鐘歸位喇！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇發覺呢幾日FB ig見到最多係咩？<br />\n熱門post又係講緊咩？<br />\n搶廁紙可樂炒口罩我唔想知啊啊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護罷工點解越嚟越少人講？<br />\n係咪成功咗大家就like share好開心<br />\n衰咗又sad陣冇咗件事咁<br />\n<br />\n<strong>醫護不是condom </strong><br />\n好多人話「我唔知有咩可以做」<br />\n首先基本嘢 全部同我推返醫護post上熱門<br />\n洗ig story連儂牆咩都好 最簡單嘅做咗先<br />\n要俾醫護知u are not alone<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其次就係！<br />\n有咩實質行動做到<br />\n好似之前人鏈、10點鳩叫令大家都效應到嘅活動<br />\n知宜家人多地方唔安全怕傳染<br />\n咁有咩係做到又安全？<br />\n一齊討論下！！<br />\n<br />\n重知係 我哋要話俾柒婆同全世界知<br />\n香港人撐醫護 我哋要封關！！！<br />\n唔淨係醫護一班人拎自己嚟作賭注<br />\n<br />\n封關救港 人人有責<br />\n<br />\n罷工第五日 亦係最後一日<br />\n同我煲大佢 煲大佢 煲大佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a31a4187aa79e06fe50390e8c388df1696adb96","tid":1867004,"uid":227979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3877f111da4ca2a5d1e6b68908e022f440804d4f","tid":1867004,"uid":227979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"我撐醫護<br />\n推"},{"pid":"74eb5dbd391cc8d9f40519866082d2dc04230f35","tid":1867004,"uid":227979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"封關救港 人人有責<br />\n推"},{"pid":"8ea3fc145a21329cbf00873dde75aa202cd39a80","tid":1867004,"uid":227979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"